title: Stainless Steel Venn Puzzle
description:
A beautiful mechanical puzzle comprising three identical pieces, die-cast in stainless steel and weighing almost 2 pounds. The Venn Puzzle is a surprisingly difficult dexterity challenge and an intriguing addition to your desk, shelf, or coffee table. The assembled puzzle creates a perfect sphere — so each piece makes up one-third of the sphere by volume. Includes assembly instructions.

  • Dimensions: 2.25 in.
  • 1.75 lbs
  • Die-cast Stainless Steel
